---
import Section from '../shared/Section.astro';
---

<Section background="primary" padding="sm">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ev-text mb-6" data-reveal>What to expect.</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4" data-reveal data-delay="100">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-sprout/5 border border-sprout/20 flex items-center justify-center text-sprout font-bold text-sm shrink-0">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-ev-text">We review your submission.</h3>
          <p class="text-ev-text-secondary text-sm">Within 24 hours. We read every project description personally.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-sprout/5 border border-sprout/20 flex items-center justify-center text-sprout font-bold text-sm shrink-0">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-ev-text">We schedule a technical conversation.</h3>
          <p class="text-ev-text-secondary text-sm">A 30-minute call to understand your domain, your timeline, and your constraints. No sales pitch. Just engineering questions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-sprout/5 border border-sprout/20 flex items-center justify-center text-sprout font-bold text-sm shrink-0">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-ev-text">We deliver an assessment.</h3>
          <p class="text-ev-text-secondary text-sm">A clear scope of work with service boundaries, timeline, and cost. If it makes sense for both sides, we begin. If it does not, you walk away with a free architecture assessment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
